          <div class="container-WhereStart">
            <div class="text-WhereStart">
              <h2>NOT SURE WHERE TO START?</h2>
              <p>
                Take our free English level assessment test to determine your
                current proficiency and get matched with suitable tutors.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="image-WhereStart">
              <img src="/imgs/anh4.jpg" alt="Student studying at a desk" />
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="container-howIt">
            <h1>HOW IT WORKS</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">
              Our simple three-step process to start learning English with
              professional tutors
            </p>
            <div class="steps">
              <div class="step">
                <h2>1. FIND YOUR TUTOR</h2>
                <p>
                  Browse our selection of professional tutors. Filter by
                  specialization, price, and availability to find your perfect
                  match.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="step">
                <h2>2. BOOK A TRIAL LESSON</h2>
                <p>
                  Schedule a discounted trial lesson to get acquainted with your
                  tutor and discuss your learning goals.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="step">
                <h2>3. START LEARNING</h2>
                <p>
                  Begin your personalized learning journey with regular lessons
                  that fit your schedule and goals.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
